</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center; padding:4pt; line-height:1.25em; text-align:center; font-size:8pt;"><a href="/wiki/File:John_Harrison_Uhrmacher.jpg" class="image" title="P.L. Tassaert's half-tone print of Thomas King's original 1767 portrait of John Harrison, located at the Science and Society Picture Library, London"><img alt="P.L. Tassaert's half-tone print of Thomas King's original 1767 portrait of John Harrison, located at the Science and Society Picture Library, London" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/12/John_Harrison_Uhrmacher.jpg/225px-John_Harrison_Uhrmacher.jpg" width="225" height="283" border="0" /></a><br />
